I. Keep NSFW content out of unmarked channels (that includes any 18+ content). II. Be civil. The discord server is mainly for discussion of the server and game, not in-game feuds or spam campaigns. III. No linking advertisements. You can advertise in-game content here, but again no links. The exception is the #ban-land channel, which is a live feed of the server chat. IV. Remember, this Discord is for discussion of the server. Rank sync is intended to facilitate discussion in a better way, and to allow more veteran players have their voices recognized. V. All Voice channels are to be considered NSFW. VI. If you need help on the server or have questions, ask in #general or make a ticket in #support. VII. No sharing or asking for identifying personal info (phone numbers, etc). General info is fine ("I'm from the USA/Europe").
